{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","text":"Integrate OUDS","level":2},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","text":"Use Swift Package Manager"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"text":", you need to add our ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"text":" into your project.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"You are free to choose wether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.18.0-rc3","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Import the librairies you need","type":"heading","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" products."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Tip"},{"code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools \/\/ To use the Orange Business Tools theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","type":"heading","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","level":3},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and useless constants."}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Import the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"text":" product which suits your needs:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above and all themes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Business Tools themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"level":3,"text":"Chose your theme","anchor":"Chose-your-theme","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" framework provides today four themes:","type":"text"}]},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Business Tools","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Apply a theme","anchor":"Apply-a-theme"},{"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes"},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"codeListing","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"numberOfColumns":2},{"numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}]}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"row"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one "},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"tip","type":"aside","name":"Tip"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"],"title":"Essentials"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted"},"kind":"article","sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"article","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"}],"title":"Getting Started with OUDS","modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Modules":{"title":"Modules","kind":"article","type":"topic","role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/modules","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_module_intro.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_module_intro.png"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"module"}]},{"text":" can be seen as a set of features and components to fill a need.","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Tokens":{"title":"Tokens","kind":"article","type":"topic","role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/tokens","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Design tokens represent the small, repeated design decisions that make up a design system’s visual style. Tokens wrap hard-coded static values, such as hexadecimal codes for color, with self-explanatory names. They are used to define the look and feel and the style of everything. They are exposed through the themes and can be used as they are.","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Components":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_component_intro.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_component_intro.png"}],"title":"Components","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/components","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" objects you can add in the views of your apps, like buttons, links, cards etc."}],"role":"article"},"https://github.com/Orange-OpenSource/ouds-ios/wiki/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","title":"refer to the wiki","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"refer to the wiki","type":"text"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds"},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/ouds/oudsthemeableview/":{"titleIn